like nothing happened.

21:42.213 --> 21:45.304
I asked Sam
if he was okay,

21:45.347 --> 21:48.176
and...he just yelled at me.

21:48.219 --> 21:50.570
"Just leave me alone.
Go!"

21:50.613 --> 21:54.095
